flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "C8A4ABD94B98E5C11080A2BA40EA9266", "I have met Valkyria, a high ranking member of the Striders Vigilant, a Verra army. She has informed me that her global force assists in the defense of Sanctus immigrants. I can do my part to assist this noble army by destroying empty crates in the nearby fields and forests. They are meant as decoys to lure Striders or local guards out to be ambushed by nearby pets of some nefarious cabal. ")
